social_posts.post_text: Year 2 starts now ∞

I came out to my closest family a decade ago. 2 years ago, I posted about being engaged. To my surprise, publications called it ‘a news anchor’s coming out’

Coming out’s not a 1 time thing. Heck, I came out to the dentist weeks ago when he asked about a wife. 

Each time, I’ve felt freer. And prouder.

There’s support all around. #NationalComingOutDay is a reminder that if you let it, love can drown out hate
Nuevo amiguito. Meet Cu (as in Cumulus ☁️)
Fall’s hottest accessory is a miniature arctic fox that’s scared of loud sounds but loves hugs
The wild Manhattan mongoose demands to be kept warm despite having its own glorious, natural fur coat
Cu is still adapting to our human customs. He does like turkey though
Love watching reports with @stephenmorgan because not only do I get encouragement, but I also get to hear what species of plants are in the background 🥰
These North Pole foxes are spreading Christmas cheer
23 was filled with glee. Let’s see what’s in store for 24 🍾🥂🎊

Happy 2024! Join me on @NBCNewsNow through noon ET 
💻 nbcnews.com/now

📺 Then on @MSNBC 12-2pm ET
